      "description": [
        "As part of the Escuelaweb development team, I delivered a range of projects in PHP, Ruby on Rails, and WordPress.",
        "These included lapatilla.com, a high-traffic news site, and embarazada.com, a web app supporting women through pregnancy.",
        "Technologies: WordPress, Ruby on Rails, JavaScript, AngularJS, Grunt, Docker, Dokku, Bootstrap, Sass, Ajax, and REST APIs."
      ]
